pharmaceutical products,

00:11:32.246 --> 00:11:34.771
including the stuff that you use
to treat arthritis,

00:11:34.795 --> 00:11:37.221
which is the number one
best-selling drug, Humira.

00:11:37.985 --> 00:11:39.436
So this lifecode stuff.

00:11:40.229 --> 00:11:41.605
It really is a superpower.

00:11:42.156 --> 00:11:44.070
It really is a way of programming stuff,

00:11:44.094 --> 00:11:46.651
and there's nothing
that's going to change us

00:11:46.675 --> 00:11:48.801
more than this lifecode.

00:11:49.597 --> 00:11:51.578
So as you're thinking of lifecode,

00:11:51.602 --> 00:11:53.291
