for this stuff.

00:12:03.042 --> 00:12:05.593
The reason we have to take responsibility

00:12:05.617 --> 00:12:06.978
is because we're in charge.

00:12:07.002 --> 00:12:08.915
These aren't random mutations.

00:12:08.939 --> 00:12:11.242
This is what we are doing,
what we are choosing.

00:12:11.266 --> 00:12:12.965
It's not, "Stuff happened."

00:12:12.989 --> 00:12:14.462
It didn't happen at random.

00:12:14.486 --> 00:12:17.090
It didn't come down
by a verdict of somebody else.

00:12:17.114 --> 00:12:18.931
We engineer this stuff,

00:12:18.955 --> 00:12:22.200
and it's the Pottery Barn rule:
you break it, you own it.

00:12:22.962 --> 00:12:24.491
Principle number two:

00:12:24.515 --> 00:12:27.643
